  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to investigate the superiority of virtual reality-supported&#xD;
      vestibular rehabilitation exercises over conventional vestibular rehabilitation exercises in&#xD;
      patients with complaints such as vertigo, loss of balance, falling, and gait imbalance.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
